casebody.head_matter:
Christopher David HARNS, petitioner,
v.
NORTH DAKOTA.
No. 14-1512.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 28, 2016.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of North Dakota. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Supreme Court of North Dakota for further consideration in light of Birchfield v. North Dakota, 579 U.S. ----, 136 S.Ct. 2160, ---L.Ed.2d ---- (2016).
